title: Disguise a Turkey- Blue Alien Blank Template Disguise- Resizable!

popular_info.title: Disguise a Turkey- Blue Alien Blank Template Disguise- Resizable!
popular_info.description: Resize this blue alien blank template disguise for your Turkey Disguise Project using Canva in order to fit your own turkey template! You will receive a PDF of the disguise which will also include a link to Canva in order to resize the disguise if needed. Written and video instructions will be provided. A turkey template is also provided in the PDF.
